a store that ran in 30 some odd countries,  

237
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:42,640
12 and a half thousand instances of the store 
doing billions of dollars of revenue. We had  

238
00:19:42,640 --> 00:19:49,520
six designers. Any other company would've 
