282
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:12,560
I want to go back to something you said 
about what design is. I think this is  

283
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:15,840
really interesting. And so the way you 
described design to a lot of people,  

284
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:20,000
it sounds like that's like product management 
also and product leadership, setting, strategy,  

285
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:24,480
vision, figuring out how everything fits 
together. I think your experience here,  

