293
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:02,880
In fact, I think that's a lot of what the design 
community is trying to get at now when they say  

294
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:06,000
designers should be speaking the language 
of business. I think what they're saying is  

295
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:11,600
designers need to inhabit the product mindset as 
