01:17:51,440 --> 01:17:54,720
but that's not really the world we're living 
in anymore. And that's not probably going to  

968
01:17:54,720 --> 01:17:59,920
suit the thing you're trying to do next, which is 
writing and publishing and speaking and stuff. And  

