01:17:59,920 --> 01:18:00,240
although it's statistically derived, it did come 
back with a really nice phrase, which I view...

970
01:18:00,240 --> 01:18:03,360
Although it's statistically derived, it 
did come back with a really nice phrase  

971
01:18:03,360 --> 01:18:08,560
which I've used in your show, which was, 
