974
01:18:17,600 --> 01:18:24,160
through most recently was I realized that it was 
inferring these things about me from the things  

975
01:18:24,160 --> 01:18:28,080
that I had asked it to help me with in the past.
So instead, I just switched. I just went to  

976
01:18:28,080 --> 01:18:33,280
ChatGPT, start a new project and said, I want 
