1047
01:23:42,880 --> 01:23:46,240
one was to build a big giant rocket and just 
go straight to the moon. It's called direct  

1048
01:23:46,240 --> 01:23:51,040
ascend. And the main advocate for that was Warner 
von Braun, who was the main rocket guy in the  

1049
01:23:51,040 --> 01:23:54,880
world. A little bit of a complicated past.
But nevertheless, Warner von Braun's a big  

1050
01:23:54,880 --> 01:23:59,120
guy. He is, got the president's ear. He's like, 
