1073
01:25:45,680 --> 01:25:49,120
do we want to go to the moon or not? And 
then he goes through all the math of how  

1074
01:25:49,120 --> 01:25:52,560
going to the moon is all about weight 
and this was the only way to do it,  

1075
01:25:52,560 --> 01:25:58,160
and there was no other option, stuff like that.
He just made the case and he risked his whole  

1076
01:25:58,160 --> 01:26:00,640
career. The whole thing could have blown up. 
He could have been fired for going around the  

1077
01:26:00,640 --> 01:26:04,160
hierarchy and all that sort of stuff, but 
of course, he's able to champion the idea. 

1078
01:26:04,160 --> 01:26:08,400
And I think it was another year or so after 
