1089
01:27:00,960 --> 01:27:04,560
champions. They need champions willing 
to put themselves on the line for them.  

1090
01:27:04,560 --> 01:27:09,200
If you believe in something and you've made 
your case and you can really make your case,  

1091
01:27:10,480 --> 01:27:15,440
